Irish McCalla https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irish_McCalla 0 Nellie Elizabeth "Irish" McCalla (December 25, 1928 – February 1, 2002) was an American actress and artist best known as the title star of the 1950s television series Sheena, Queen of the Jungle. Sheena co-starred with actor Chris Drake. McCalla was also a "Vargas Girl" model for pinup girl artist Alberto Vargas.
